                           <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__muschel_jude_QGW_II_I_605">Hausfrau</roleName></rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__smoyel_jude_QGW_II_I_1564">Smoyel der Jud, [der Juden <roleName type="title">sanchmaister</roleName>]</rs>, und <rs type="person" ref="pe__paetzel_QGW_II_I_605">Paeczel, seine <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__smoyel_jude_QGW_II_I_1564">Hausfrau</roleName></rs></rs>,
