                     <rs type="person" ref="pe__johann_von_tierna_QGW_II_I_1018"><roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Jansen von Tyrnach, pürgermaister<roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien"><add>purgermaister</add></roleName> und
